high_descs: Walk over to the sink on the right.
Pick up the egg from the right side of the sink.
Turn around and walk straight to the fridge.
Put the egg on the top shelf in the fridge, close the door, open the door, take the egg out of the fridge, close the door.
Walk over to the counter with the microwave on it to the left.
Open the microwave door, put the egg down to the right of the plate, close the microwave door.
anns.task_desc: To chill an egg and put it in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn to the left and go to the sink.
Pick up the egg from the sink.
Turn around and go to the fridge.
Place the egg in the fridge. Let it chill a moment then take it out.
Turn to the right and go forward. Turn to the left and face the microwave.
Place the egg inside the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Chill then place an egg in the microwave.

high_descs: Make a left to walk to the sink.
Pick up the egg from the sink.
Turn around to walk to the fridge.
Chill the egg in the freezer, removing it again.
Make a right to walk to the microwave.
Put the egg in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Chill an egg in the freezer to put in the microwave.
